Reasoning: The paper discusses predicting the popularity of online content, specifically news articles, using time series forecasting. This involves analyzing article similarity and topicality, which suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of time series forecasting indicates a potential focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.SI). Finally, the use of real data from an international news website suggests a potential focus on social media analysis (cs.SD).
